{"tid":1469344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不做被仇恨支配的人","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:14:54.000Z","uid":301754,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ae22c993d56701dec3b6fe62ebb9e98c591c4e94","tid":1469344,"uid":301754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WjYTQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WjYTQQ.jpg&h=7b3c0309&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0f5yQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0f5yQQ.jpg&h=c9af4320&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDuh9pb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDuh9pb.jpg&h=7dc3129b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場圈套已入</span></span>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">破壞已不能制止</span></span>，<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就先放過呢張機場牌</span></span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">休息是要走更遠的路</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZpcPf58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpcPf58.jpg&h=d37303e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3fc24a40fd796626048eb3bcac90fff7979b015","tid":1469344,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:32:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過812同813我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"24fe19af00f0b2b9e8cef341b22f5f5e614d0fdb","tid":1469344,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bfe79d1b3caa7ab45bc3c229281ef5a24fe473","tid":1469344,"uid":301754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:42:50.000Z","msg":"政府一早寫好的劇本：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派公安混入示威者<br />\n2. 故意挑起事端<br />\n3. 用任何原因令自己受傷害<br />\n4. 警察故意容許及消失<br />\n5. 製造輿論（重點是在內地的媒體）<br />\n5. 頭條：「中國公民無故被港獨恐怖分子圍毆，警察無能為力，必須派解放軍保護居港的中國人民。」<br />\n6. 如果唔得，由第一點開始再來過<br />\n<br />\n類似劇本30年前已經上演過，今晚，狠人認為機場明顯再陷入了這個圈套！<br />\n<br />\n#永不割蓆<br />\n#勿忘初心<br />\n#香港人加油"},{"pid":"dae1e6602718ca3feef8dc045e1b36c8f7b783c2","tid":1469344,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:14:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">612<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n勿忘同行手足的付出 傷痕<br />\n五大訴求 <br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"}]}